{"tid":2515642,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【事主相片曝光】11歲女玩手機game 遇鹹濕網友求裸照","createTime":"2021-05-04T06:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T07:22:39.000Z","uid":38539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"45c33ec1dced925a75b3f0652755c35228973947","tid":2515642,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:32:28.000Z","msg":"一名11歲女童早前透過手機遊戲應用程式認識一名男網友，該男網友除了與女童展開性討論，更向女童分享不雅照片，並要求她分享其不雅裸照，該女童家人知悉事件後報案。<br />\n<br />\n深水埗警區刑事調查隊經過深入調查後，昨日下午分別在屯門區及深水埗區拘捕一名18歲男子及其45歲母親，涉嫌「向青少年發布不雅物品」。調查顯示，兩人分別為懷疑涉案媒體賬戶的用戶及該部電話的登記人。兩人已獲准保釋候查，須於六月上旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n警方提醒家長應加多留意子女的網上行為，切勿讓子女輕易相信來歷不明的信息，更不要隨便回應陌生人的要求，免墜社交媒體陷阱。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmU9RPxMsz2rad8jiuZniP8vQUwokzgxt4AB9Xb8Vy9eWf?filename=h7Dxqki.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh7Dxqki.png&h=9230b3d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n18歲男網友昨被警員拘捕帶走。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210504/R3KWZNIJUZHKVIIDDQCRZX4VNQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210504%2FR3KWZNIJUZHKVIIDDQCRZX4VNQ%2F&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGntOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=4ceb048e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210504%2FR3KWZNIJUZHKVIIDDQCRZX4VNQ%2F&h=b2df1f22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210504/R3KWZNIJUZHKVIIDDQCRZX4VNQ/</a>"},{"pid":"6ae2e9db954e7c91b525d2c3d851dd6988b74d34","tid":2515642,"uid":378793,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:34:41.000Z","msg":"矮仔心理變態"},{"pid":"629a297330c7b43c2228892255bd6f733919c0d3","tid":2515642,"uid":29620,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:35:03.000Z","msg":"邊位巴打?"},{"pid":"d679cbbd1e48bacc12ca567a9e34233d6c862dbd","tid":2515642,"uid":180302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:35:48.000Z","msg":"等日做狗就冇事"},{"pid":"4c84